{"tid":1068902,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇天下一未來幾年嘅電影？","createTime":"2019-03-19T14:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T18:16:19.000Z","uid":37358,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f281d7a111d1728317d476f59a362ca593ae6a90","tid":1068902,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"天下一電影自成立後秉承以創新方向及想法，為香港電影帶來新血及衝擊。天下一於今天在香港會議展覽中心的香港國際影視展上舉行了「2019 天下一電影巡禮」，向業界及傳媒朋友展示今年天下一將開發、投資、製作及發行的電影作品，當中包括《明日戰記》、 《尋秦記》、《風雲》、《犯罪現場》、《守闕者》、《媽媽的神奇小子》、《雞蛋仔》、 《紙皮婆婆》、《電影痴漢》、《BABY 復仇記》等等。 發佈會現場上星光熠熠，出席影星及監製、導演眾多，包括:古天樂、劉青雲、劉嘉玲、宣萱、林峯、吳君如、張繼聰、顏卓靈、姜皓文、薛凱琪、譚耀文、安志杰、劉心悠、吳肇軒、李璨琛、林家棟、陳靜、朱鑑然、廖子妤、周國賢、郭羨妮、雪兒、滕麗名、爾冬陞、吳炫輝、黎震龍、馮志強、羅耀輝、陸以心、徐梓耀、尹志文等。<br />\n<br />\n利申：幾期待犯罪現場同電影痴漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/onecoolfilm/posts/2364533490231872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fonecoolfilm%2Fposts%2F2364533490231872&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=19bb0e91\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/onecoolfilm/posts/2364533490231872</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tc3YuMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftc3YuMr.jpg&h=a4c80522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n犯罪現場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxP49MA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxP49MA.jpg&h=6bf9ab43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明日戰記<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfdhLj4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfdhLj4.jpg&h=af918db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋秦記<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPUMDFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbPUMDFe.jpg&h=2a51c251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影痴漢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrXB0TH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrXB0TH.jpg&h=88f176cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBABY 復仇記<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33o2b0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33o2b0v.jpg&h=8366d97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雞蛋仔"},{"pid":"43caeab9602d617906c048230c88972ad0ffdd32","tid":1068902,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"古仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1e826c133c9d34a7adf35e9610878b3838e8ed","tid":1068902,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b8fc283b1edefb7a070e4ddcc5c111883b9f759c","tid":1068902,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"最期待一定係尋秦記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101c7efeb5359882433203ac239a652a6894131e","tid":1068902,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T18:16:19.000Z","msg":"都叫好肯試新題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}